      "span_text": "Then, assuming we want to abstract from intermediate species, multi-stage and multi-path transformations can be modeled using respectively Erlang and Hyperexponential distributions with parameters equal to the ones reported in Tab.  Note that we model the transformation with probability distributions that have the same expected value but different variances."
